# Telegram Group Management System Architecture

## System Overview
A comprehensive Telegram group management platform built with Next.js, focusing on group administration, activity management, and commission tracking.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend Framework**: Next.js
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- **State Management**: React Context/Hooks
- **UI/UX**: Responsive Design + Dark/Light Theme

